data.description: Assumable VA Loan available. Discover the priceless joy of owning this gorgeous 5 bedroom home plus a guest's quarter with panoramic mountain views! Inviting interior boasts tile flooring, high ceilings, a living & dining room, and a large family room with a cozy stove fireplace. Spotless kitchen display recessed lighting, cabinets with crown moulding, essential appliances, granite counters, a 2-tiered island, and a breakfast nook. Generous-sized main retreat features plush carpet, two walk-in closets, and an elegant ensuite with dual sinks. You'll also have a 400 sqft guest's quarter with a private bathroom. Hang out in the huge backyard providing a covered patio, storage shed, multiple-seating areas, fire pit, and incredible mountain views! This value has two separate garages, a 1200 sq ft and a 1500 sg ft building that can hold a total of 10 cars, along with a 1000 sq ft breezeway, a covered 24 x 24 parking area, a 400 sq ft welding room and 200 amp service and RV hookups on 4.2 acres. Truly a must-see!
